   1. Log shows 7 "NOTE: [one_year <yr>] rows=" lines, each ~15M+.
   2. csv_staging holds hmda_2019.csv .. hmda_2025.csv with plausible sizes
      (multi-GB each; a KB-scale file means a silent failure).
   3. Spot-check one header, e.g. in SAS:
        data _null_; infile "&csv_dir\hmda_2025.csv" obs=1; input; put _infile_; run;
